---
title: Indian Style Spiced Halloumi Hash with Mango Chutney, Tomato and Mint Raita
description: Pile up roasted potatoes, dressed tomatoes and glazed halloumi before drizzling over homemade mint raita for this Indian Style Spiced Halloumi Hash to make a bowl full of colour and warming flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R22_W45_UK_V16958-4_Main_low-455b31e6.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/66d71654cc7423314feb89a7-en-GB.pdf
time required: 40 minutes
course: main course
servings: 2
cuisine: Indian
author: Lily Stevens
